<!--Code-->
Code: ```2016 (0x7E0)```
<!--Text-->
Text: ```"The properties of the disk drive doesn't match the database image (is the disk drive is configured for a different sector size than the image is built for?)."```
<!--AutoGenerated/-->

_There is currently no further description available._
### Example
_There is currently no code example available on how to reproduce error 2016. Please modify the code below in a way that can describe how to produce this error._

```csharp
using Starcounter;
using System;

class Program {
    static void Main(string[] args) {
        // Foo can not be successfully invoked if PreFoo() is not
        // invoked previously. If Foo() is called like this, it will
        // generate an error 2016.
        Db.Foo();
    }
}
```

### Resolution
_There is currently no code example available on how to remedy error 2016. Please modify the code below in a way that can describe how to remedy this error._

```csharp
using Starcounter;
using System;

class Program {
    static void Main(string[] args) {
        // We call PreFoo() prior to calling Foo(). Now, we will
        // no longer experience error 2016.
        Db.PreFoo();
        Db.Foo();
    }
}
```
